# AVAsyncProperty.Status.loaded(_:)

**Case**

A property value is ready to use.

## Declaration

```swift
case loaded(Value)
```

## Parameters

- **value**: A value for the property.

## Status values

- **AVAsyncProperty.Status.notYetLoaded**: The system hasn’t loaded a property value.
- **AVAsyncProperty.Status.loading**: The system is loading the property.
- **AVAsyncProperty.Status.failed(_:)**: A property value fails to load.
